  "title": {
   "en": "Tsuihou Sareta Ossan Kajishi, Nazeka Densetsu no Daimyouko ni Naru ~Mukashi Omocha no Buki o Tsukutteageta Kodomotachi ga Zenin Eiyuu ni Natteita~"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "追放されたおっさん鍛冶師、なぜか伝説の大名工になる ～昔おもちゃの武器を造ってあげた子供たちが全員英雄になっていた～"
   },
   {
    "ja-ro": "Tsuihou sareta Ossan Kajishi, Nazeka Densetsu no Daimyouko ni Naru: Mukashi Omocha no Buki wo Tsukutteageta Kodomotachi ga Zenin Eiyuu ni Natteita"
   },
   {
    "en": "The Expelled Middle-Aged Blacksmith Somehow Becomes a Legendary Famous Craftsman: The Kids Who He Once Made Some Toy Weapons for Have All Become Heroes"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "40-year-old Dereito has dedicated his life to blacksmithing in a small town, but one day, he is suddenly expelled by his fellow guild members. \n\nWith nowhere to go, he remembers a letter he received from a young girl for whom he once crafted a “toy weapon” and decides to head to the royal capital. Upon arrival, he discovers that the “toy weapon” he had made has evolved into a legendary weapon, and the girl has become a national hero! \n\nHis life turns around from being an unemployed middle-aged man to being celebrated as the hero who crafted a legendary weapon. To his surprise, he reunites with the colleagues who had cast him out in an unexpected way, eventually taking them on as his apprentices!",
   "ja": "地方都市で鍛冶一筋、40歳の主人公デレートは、ある日突然ギルドの同僚に追放されてしまう。\n\nそこで以前「おもちゃの武器」を造ってあげていた女の子からもらった手紙を頼りに王都へ向かうと、自分が作った「おもちゃの武器」が伝説の武器に進化しており、その子は国の英雄になっていた!\n\n無職のおっさん(40)から一転、伝説の武器を作った英雄として大出世!\nさらに自分を追い出した同僚と意外な形で再会し、弟子として迎え入れることに!?"
  },
